      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LIGHTNING TIGER (7) box seated before sticking on well to finish half a length away in third (17.96) at this track in a Maiden over 324m. Can find winning form. SHOW MORE (8) had to overcome traffic and was hampered for a run before finishing a distant third (18.07) in a Maiden over 324m at this track. Worth following up. ANJO STATUE (1) held his own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only a neck (17.95) behind Pay Me at this track. Expected to be in this for a long way. ABSCONDING (5) is a newcomer from the Kristy Sultana kennel. No favours with the draw and will need to begin well. Market to provide the best guide to his chances.",
